						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">tokumaru wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Most of the time, 8KB is too much for save data, but since Nintendo already used 8KB RAM chips for CHR-RAM it was probably easier/cheaper for them to use the same chip than to go with something smaller.</div>
